Pre-Performance Rituals
  Before Playing
    Be Well-Rested
      To reduce tilt and increase performance
    Eat if Hungry
      To reduce tilt and increase performance
    Clean your room (specifically your desk) for 25 minutes
      To increase equipment performance and to make you start cleaning
    Shower
      So you don’t arbitrarily destroy your body
    Stretch Arms and Back
      To reduce the chance of injury and increase performance
      Spend 10 minutes researching stretches
    Play 3 osu! Songs
      To increase the amount of information your eyes register
      To increase your clicking speed and precision
      One on easy, one on medium and one on hard
    Psych yourself up
      Find motivation from somewhere that isn’t misery
      Practice talking to yourself in a non-negative way

